    <details class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5"><summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">Can I compare cities before becoming a digital nomad?</summary><p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Yes. Use the Cost of Living Comparison tool alongside the Digital Nomad Calculator to compare monthly living costs, one-time setup fees, and your likely break-even timeline.</p></details>
